snippet: After President Vladimir V. Putin, in a motorized hang glider, led six Siberian cranes on the first leg of a migration flight, they proved unable to complete the trip as winter approaches.
abstract: Six Siberian cranes that were led on first leg of migration by Russian Pres Vladimir V Putin,  who used motorized hang glider, are returned to captivity after being unable to finish their trip as winter approaches.
lead_paragraph: After President Vladimir V. Putin, in a motorized hang glider, led six Siberian cranes on the first leg of a migration flight, they proved unable to complete the trip as winter approaches.

headline.seo: Putin’s Cranes Fail to Migrate and Turn Back
headline.main: A Flock Too Stubborn for Even Putin to Control
headline.print_headline: A Flock That’s Too Stubborn For Even Putin to Control
